<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink384">
<l>cēṭpula muṉṉiya vacainaṭai yantaṇir</l>
<l>nummoṉ ṟirantaṉeṉ moḻiva lemmūr</l>
<l>yāynayan teṭutta vāynalaṅ kaviṉa</l>
<l>vāriṭai yiṟantaṉa ḷeṉmi</l>
<l>ṉēriṟai muṉkaiyeṉ ṉāyat tōrkkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O brahmins of slow pace, thinking of distant lands! </l>
<l>I humbly ask you for one thing. In our village, </l>
<l>tell my friends with fine forearms, </l>
<l>that she has traversed harsh places to enhance select beauty, </l>
<l>lovingly nurtured by my mother. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
